OL,3,CUnion nurse members accept pay offer
OL,4,Cfrom Manx Care
OL,6,FUnion nurse members in the have voted
OL,7,Fto accept a 6% pay rise, offered by
OL,8,FManx Care.
OL,10,FMembers of the Royal College of
OL,11,FNursing were surveyed between 31
OL,12,FJanuary and 14 February 2024 on the
OL,13,Flatest pay offer which dates back to
OL,14,Flast April.
OL,16,FA total of 75% of voting members
OL,17,Faccepted while 25% rejected the terms.
