OL,3,CUnion nurse members accept pay offer
OL,4,Cfrom Manx Care
OL,6,FEstephanie Dunn, Director for the RCN
OL,7,Fin the North West, said: "Thank you to
OL,8,FthoseJmembers who took the time to
OL,9,Fvote, it's really important that we
OL,10,Fhave a strong voice so that our
OL,11,Fresponse is clear to the employer.
OL,13,F"I am pleased that we have reached a
OL,14,Fresolution quickly to this offer
OL,15,Fhowever, we now await the results of
OL,16,Fthe other union surveys to see if the
OL,17,Fmajority has accepted.
OL,19,F"We now must see our members receive
OL,20,Fthis pay rise as soon as possible."
