OL,3,CUnion nurse members accept pay offer
OL,4,Cfrom Manx Care
OL,6,FThe pay agreement will be applied once
OL,7,Fall the unions have concluded their
OL,8,Fresults.
OL,10,FDespite agreeing to the pay
OL,11,Fconditions, the RCN has expressed
OL,12,Fconcern over the lack of clarity in
OL,13,Fwhether it will include back-pay for
OL,14,Fnurses who left Manx Care before the
OL,15,Foffered was made.
OL,17,FMs Dunn has encouraged those who left
OL,18,FManx Care from April 2023 to submit an
OL,19,Fappeal to allow themselves to be
OL,20,Fconsidered for back-pay in the time
OL,21,Fthey worked there.
