OL,6,FShe said: "They have worked the hours
OL,7,Fand deserve to be paid at the full
OL,8,Frate they should have been paid
OL,9,Fanyway, plus any pension
OL,10,Fcontributions, had this offer been
OL,11,Freceived and accepted before the pay
OL,12,Fyear commenced."
OL,14,FManx Care has set up an appeal process
OL,15,Fso individual cases can be considered
OL,16,Ffor back-pay.
OL,18,FHowever, staff must still have a
OL,19,Fconnection with the trust such as bank
OL,20,Fwork, to be eligible.
